# Agent-loop instructions

Work autonomously on one assigned GitHub issue. Read this file and the issue,
then implement, validate, refactor, and commit locally. Stop after the local
commit. Do not push, open a pull request, or invoke Gemini, Copilot, `reviewit`,
or any GitHub-hosted AI reviewer; the wrapper owns review and publication.

> Customize every `TODO` before using the loop. This consumer-owned file is
> bootstrapped once and is not overwritten by later syncs.

